cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.DL, cs.DB

The paper deals with the extraction of social networks of organizations from PubMed abstracts, which involves natural language processing and data mining techniques. This falls under the scope of information retrieval (cs.IR) and social network analysis (cs.SI). The paper also involves text classification and clustering (cs.CL), as well as machine learning and data management (cs.DL, cs.DB).
